(14987, 'Vincent Van Gogh\\\'s Starry Night is well known for its coloring - the bright and vivid stars in contrast to the dark tones of the night sky. This visual information is being evaluated by means of which of the following criteria?', 'A: Use of colors', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
