(15017, 'A famous boyband has been the face of a brand of an alcoholic drink for years. This is an example of _____.', 'A: Celebrity endorsements', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
(15018, 'Dove released a commercial, entitled, “Evolution\\ that depicts a model groomed to be the face of an advertisement. Her face became the focal point of the whole video that you can see how her look changed from make up to digital photo enhancements until she ended up on a billboard ad for make-up. What type of propaganda is used for this commercial?', 'A: Transfer', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
(15019, 'Stop motion animation is also known as which of the following?', 'A: Object animation', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
