(15021, 'President Duterte’s continuous campaign of the war against drugs is an example of propaganda.', 'A: False', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
(15022, 'A banned Pepsi commercial made the rounds on the internet in the early 2000s. It shows a young boy who wanted to buy soda from a vending machine. In this commercial, the kid bought two cans of Coca-Cola. He stood on top of these cans, boosting his height for him to reach the button for Pepsi. This commercial is an example of ____.', 'A: Card-stacking', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
(15023, 'Which of the following techniques makes use of a transparent sheet of paper on which objects are drawn?', 'A: Cel animation', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
