(15098, 'Lin-Manuel Miranda, the author of the Tony Award-winning Broadway musical entitled “Hamilton,\\ was of Puerto Rican descent. Recently, Hurricane Maria devastated Puerto Rico and Miranda was intent on helping his fellowmen. He released a song called “Almost Like Praying\\ that featured Latino artists such as Jennifer Lopez, Gloria Estefan, Camila Cabello, among others, and the sales of the single would be for the hurrican relief. What media manipulation technique did Miranda use?', 'A: Celebrity Endorsement', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
