(15100, 'A visual novel is an example of which of the following?', 'A: interactive multimedia', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
(15101, 'What is the drawback of choosing newspaper as an advertising medium?', 'A: It is only accurate for the day or week, and may be discarded as soon as possible after distribution', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
