(15112, 'The 2012 Tim Burton film Frankenweenie made use of puppets in order to come up with animated scenes. What kind of animation technique has been used in the creation of the film?', 'A: Stop-motion ', 'MEIL-122 (Media and Information Literacy)', NULL),
