(17052, 'A bucket in an old well is hoisted upward by a rope which winds up on a cylinder having a radius of 0.050 m. How many rev/s must the cylinder turn if the bucket is raised at a speed of 0.15 m/s?', '0.48 rev/s', 'PHYC-121 (Physics)', NULL),
(17053, 'A 2500-kg truck moving at 10.00 m/s strikes a car waiting at a traffic light, hooking bumpers. The two continue to move together at 6.00 m/s. What was the mass of the struck car?', '1670 kg	', 'PHYC-121 (Physics)', NULL),
